# Web3Forms access key for the contact form.
# Get a free key at https://web3forms.com — enter info@abbottsolicitors.com (or
# whichever address should receive enquiries) as the destination, confirm via
# the verification email Web3Forms sends, and paste the key below.
#
# This value is inlined into the client bundle at build time (NEXT_PUBLIC_*
# prefix), which is intentional — the access key is designed to be public and
# only authorises POSTs to the destination configured on web3forms.com.
#
# Local dev: copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the key.
# Production (Azure Static Web Apps): set the GitHub repo secret
# `WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY` — the deploy workflow exposes it as
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY at build time.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
